  <brief_title>A Study of SK-1405 in Hemodialysis Patients With Uremic Pruritus</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II, Double-Blind, Randomized, Placebo-Controlled Study of SK-1405 in Hemodialysis Patients With Uremic Pruritus</official_title>
