  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the efficacy, safety and dose response of SK-1405
      for the treatment of subjects with uremic pruritus receiving hemodialysis, during 2 weeks of
      treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
